headline: Air Products' New Cleveland Air Separation Facility and Liquefier Onstream and Supplying Onsite and Regional Customers
summary: Air Products (NYSE: APD), a leading global industrial gas supplier, today announced that its new air separation facility in Cleveland, Ohio is onstream and supplying customers. Air Products built, owns and operates the new facility which includes liquid production capability.
